text: Trump aide Ja'Ron Smith, the highest-ranking Black official in the White House: "In the wake of the murder of Breonna Taylor, George Floyd, and LeGend Taliferro — a moment of national racial consciousness — I have seen his true conscience." https://t.co/lfNacWJICu
